  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Appeteaser offers endless fun with wave and arena shooters spiced with mini games. You will fight a horde of various zombies with different kind of ranged and melee weapons. You can collect points to unlock new guns, levels and power ups.It is an easy going fun in which you can jump in any time and enjoy a bit of mayhem. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074490/extras/224a504d9b1e370aa1bea296794cc4bb.webp?t=1729506424\" width=600 height=51 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074490/extras/09d0e4828fcc333d3220dd26ba6ff7fd.poster.avif?t=1729506424\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074490/extras/09d0e4828fcc333d3220dd26ba6ff7fd.webm?t=1729506424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074490/extras/09d0e4828fcc333d3220dd26ba6ff7fd.mp4?t=1729506424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074490/extras/b7d0a74467ce0aabfb4f90efc0863351.webp?t=1729506424\" width=600 height=51 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074490/extras/f6aa3bf4bfd215c84531183d391c661b.poster.avif?t=1729506424\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074490/extras/f6aa3bf4bfd215c84531183d391c661b.webm?t=1729506424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.ak